, \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 2963}, {\"ngram\": \"marginalized communities\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"the backdrop\", \"from\": 3013, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"a global sporting event\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Critics argue that while the Olympics promise economic benefits and cultural exchange, they should not come at the expense of human rights and social justice.\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Critics\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3062}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3092}, {\"ngram\": \"economic benefits\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3118}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural exchange\", \"from\": 3123, \"to\": 3140}, {\"ngram\": \"the expense\", \"from\": 3166, \"to\": 3177}, {\"ngram\": \"human rights\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3193}, {\"ngram\": \"social justice\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In response to inquiries, local authorities cited safety concerns and legal irregularities as justification for the eviction, asserting their commitment to upholding the law.\", \"from\": 3215, \"to\": 3389, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"response\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"inquiries\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3239}, {\"ngram\": \"local authorities\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3258}, {\"ngram\": \"safety concerns\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3280}, {\"ngram\": \"legal irregularities\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3305}, {\"ngram\": \"justification\", \"from\": 3309, \"to\": 3322}, {\"ngram\": \"the eviction\", \"from\": 3327, \"to\": 3339}, {\"ngram\": \"their commitment\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3367}, {\"ngram\": \"the law\", \"from\": 3381, \"to\": 3388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, calls for a more compassionate and sustainable approach to addressing homelessness and housing insecurity persist, with activists urging policymakers to prioritize long-term solutions over short-term aesthetic improvements.\", \"f